    "figure 11 presents the top 80 bigram frequencies.",
    "An analysis of the trigrams unveils themes such as \"artificial intelligence help\", \"using artificial intelligence\", and \"impact artificial intelligence\" underscoring a focus on the usage of the technology and its impact across multiple domains.",
    "Delving into the quadrams unravels intricate themes found in our dataset.",
    "Phrases such as \"things ai missed today\",\"artificial intelligence health market\", and \"ai ethics ai law\" showcase a nuanced discourse where these factors play a crucial role.",
